---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Dario Mory";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp"/>
    </div>
    <h1>Dario Mory</h1>
    <small>Engineering Leader</small> 
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        In my journey as a digital craftsman and founder, I've found a genuine fascination in weaving together full-stack solutions. Guided by a curiosity for emerging tech trends, I focus on creating meaningful and efficient outcomes, always learning and growing alongside my team in this ever-evolving tech landscape.
    </p>
    <p>
        In the dynamic world of software development, my focus is on delivering smart, effective solutions. I believe in teamwork and continuous learning to stay ahead in the tech field. My goal is to keep projects innovative, impactful, and aligned with the latest industry trends.
    </p>
    <div class="button">
        <a href="/works/">
            <button class="button">My portfolio</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="link-images">
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="C#" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="C#" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/react/react-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="C#" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/vuejs/vuejs-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="C#" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/cplusplus/cplusplus-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="C#" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/csharp/csharp-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="TypeScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/typescript/typescript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="JavaScript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="MongoDB" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/mongodb/mongodb-original.svg"/>
    </div>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
       Constantly diving into the latest tech advancements, contributing to meaningful projects, and engaging with the tech community. At meetings and conventions, I enjoy sharing ideas and connecting with fellow enthusiasts, offering a glimpse into the vibrant and ever-evolving world of technology.
    </p>
</Layout>
<style>
    /* small */
    small {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
    }

    /* Button */
    button {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
        border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #fdebf3;
        font: 600 16px 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #78c2ad;
        color: #1e1e2e;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
        margin: 16px 4px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .link-images img {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin: 16px 1px;
        }
    }
</style>
